    dc:description "Figure 1. (A) Body of Bannatettix brevipennis Deng, Zheng et Wei, 2008, lateral view; (B) body of Bannatettix menghaiensis Zheng, 1993, lateral view; (C) head of Bannatettix menghaiensis Zheng, 1993, frontal view; (D) body of Bannatettix longqishanensis Zheng, 1993, lateral view; (E) body of Bannatettix ruiliensis Zheng, 1993, lateral view; (F) body of Bannatettix serrifemoralis Zheng and Shi, 2009, lateral view; (G) body of Bannatettix guangxiensis Zheng and Jiang, 1997, lateral view; (H) body of Bannatettix longqishanensis Zheng, 1993, dorsal view; (I) body of Bannatettix tianlinensis Zheng, Jiang and Liu, 2005, dorsal view; (J) body of Bannatettix nigritibialis Zheng and Shi, 2009, lateral view; (K) body of Bannatettix tenuifemura Deng, Zheng et Wei, 2008, lateral view." ;
